By Kadiri Abdulrahman The Tinubu Vanguard, a political support group, has commended President Muhammadu Buhari for enabling a “level playing field” in the All Progressives Congress (APC) presidential primary election. Dr Johnny Benjamin, the Director-General of the group, said this in a statement on Thursday, in a congratulatory message to the party’s National Leader, Bola Tinubu. The News Agency of Nigeria (NAN) reports that Tinubu Vanguard is a support group for the presidential aspiration of Tinubu. Benjamin described Tinubu’s success at the primary election as a well deserved victory. He also commended the leadership of the APC for a well organised primary election. “Your emergence is a sure victory for the APC at 2023 general elections. “President Muhammadu Buhari deserves special commendation for providing the right leadership for the party by allowing a free, fair and credible democratic process. “The National Working Committee of the APC, all functionaries of the party, security agencies, the media and other stakeholders also deserve commendation,” he said. He called on all the stakeholders to redouble their efforts by committing themselves to victory for Tinubu in the 2023 presidential poll. (NAN)(www.nannews.ng) ============ Edited by Muhammad Suleiman Tola